headline: Waste Management (WM): Assessing Valuation After Recent Period of Flat Share Price Movement
summary: Waste Management (WM) has stayed on investors’ radar as its share price showed minor movement in recent days, closing at $216.46. Over the past month, returns have been relatively flat, even as the company reported steady annual growth in both revenue and net income. See our latest analysis for Waste Management. Zooming out, Waste Management’s solid share price return of 7.9% year-to-date hints at steady investor confidence, especially given the company’s strong three- and five-year total...
